{"id": "36483", "revid": "773742", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=36483", "title": "Anniversary Gift", "text": "Anniversary Gift is a for &lt;a href=\"Khalid\"&gt;Khalid&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nAcquisition.\nKhalid does not need to be in the party to begin or complete this quest. It can be acquired by speaking to Khalid after resolving the siege of &lt;a href=\"Bridgefort\"&gt;Bridgefort&lt;/a&gt;, either near the end of or at the &lt;a href=\"Coalition%20Camp\"&gt;Coalition Camp&lt;/a&gt; in . He asks first for some &lt;a href=\"Spider%20Silk\"&gt;Spider Silk&lt;/a&gt;, and then an &lt;a href=\"Aquamarine%20Gem\"&gt;Aquamarine Gem&lt;/a&gt;, as part of his plans to create a wedding anniversary present for his wife, &lt;a href=\"Jaheira\"&gt;Jaheira&lt;/a&gt;. It may require multiple conversations to trigger the right topics to begin or continue this quest.\nWalkthrough.\n&lt;a href=\"Spider%20Silk\"&gt;Spider Silk&lt;/a&gt; can be found either in the &lt;a href=\"Spider%20Cave\"&gt;Spider Cave&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Forest%20of%20Wyrms\"&gt;Forest of Wyrms&lt;/a&gt; in Chapter Nine, or in a hidden cellar subregion of &lt;a href=\"Dead%20Man%27s%20Pass\"&gt;Dead Man's Pass&lt;/a&gt; in Chapter Ten. An &lt;a href=\"Aquamarine%20Gem\"&gt;Aquamarine Gem&lt;/a&gt; can be found in several locations, but the first opportunity is on the body of an &lt;a href=\"ettin\"&gt;ettin&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Dead%20Man%27s%20Pass\"&gt;Dead Man's Pass&lt;/a&gt; in Chapter Ten.\nReward.\nIf &lt;a href=\"Khalid\"&gt;Khalid&lt;/a&gt; is asked for financial compensation for retrieving the aquamarine, he will part with . When some time has passed after giving both items to Khalid, Jaheira will begin a conversation if she is in the party or trigger one next time she is spoken to in which she will reveal the present that Khalid fashioned for her, expressing her own love for it and him no matter what the player says about it. This grants her &lt;a href=\"The%20Gift\"&gt;The Gift&lt;/a&gt;, a unique &lt;a href=\"necklace\"&gt;necklace&lt;/a&gt; that grants her +10 hit points, +1 Charisma, and immunity to &lt;a href=\"fatigue\"&gt;fatigue&lt;/a&gt;."}
