{"id": "56177", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=56177", "title": "Apprentice (Carston)", "text": "The Apprentice is a male human mage, found in the &lt;a href=\"Watcher%27s%20Keep%20Illithid%20Encampment\"&gt;Watcher's Keep Illithid Encampment&lt;/a&gt; in a cell. \nHe is stricken with physical and mental wounds and near death.\nGameplay.\nIn the central part of this illithid dungeon level are several cells that can be investigated. \nOne of these is inhabited by a human male, lying prone on the floor, who it appears is seriously abused and wounded, and who's every breath sounds labored and shallow.\nInitiate dialogue with the man, and eventually he croaks out a response.\nThis man is one of Carston's apprentices that took part in the exploration of Watcher's Keep a decade ago. \nThis particular mage managed to survive the ordeal, which can be better understood if the party engages in non-threatening and patient dialogue.\nEventually, the apprentice was seized and captured by the illithids, who have systematically tortured him physically and psychically - trying to wrest information from him.\nThe apprentice knows the secret to opening Carston's glass cage, but he is determined to never let him free.\nWhatever secrets the apprentice retains are defiantly not revealed to anyone, but some clues can be had with patient dialogue choices. Being angry or short with him will just hasten his demise, closing off further potential information.\nGain as much information as possible from the apprentice, before he lets slip the mortal coil and perishes before you.\nAs Carston's former apprentice embraces the darkness, each party member receives and the player's Journal registers the following: "}
{"id": "47859", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=47859", "title": "Apprentice Torturer Douglas", "text": "Apprentice Torturer Douglas is a young child found in the torture chamber that's located within &lt;a href=\"Aran%20Linvail%27s%20Hideout\"&gt;Aran Linvail's Hideout&lt;/a&gt;. He's working under the tutelage of the gnomish prison torturer &lt;a href=\"Booter\"&gt;Booter&lt;/a&gt; and regretting his apprenticeship. "}
