{"id": "11209", "revid": "53053884", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11209", "title": "Arrow of Piercing", "text": "Arrows of Piercing (Arrow of Piercing +1 in-game) are magic arrows which appear throughout the &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt; series. They provide a +4 THAC0 boost and deal an additional 6 points of &lt;a href=\"Piercing%20damage\"&gt;Piercing damage&lt;/a&gt; if the target fails a Save vs. Death."}
