{"id": "43161", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43161", "title": "B1-12M4.ITM", "text": "This item is used by various creatures in the game, and in addition to considerable damage and high enchantment (is not affected by &lt;a href=\"Improved%20Mantle\"&gt;Improved Mantle&lt;/a&gt;) it instils panic on a successful hit. The panic can be avoided by a successful save vs. spell or immunity against &lt;a href=\"Panic\"&gt;Panic&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "52071", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52071", "title": "B1-2.ITM", "text": "B1-2.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by various creatures.\nIt is considered a non-magical and unenchanted item and applies 1d2 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nThis item may represent a fist or other nontraditional weapon blow. However, it inflicts actual crushing damage, and not \"stunning\" or subdual damage like a player characters naked fist would cause.\nIt has no animation assigned and other effects."}
{"id": "50045", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50045", "title": "B1-20M3.ITM", "text": "B1-20M2.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by various Lesser Air Elemental creatures.\nIt is considered a magical and +3 enchanted item and deals 1d20 damage (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no other effects."}
{"id": "51287", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51287", "title": "B1-4.ITM", "text": "B1-4.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by some &lt;a href=\"Mephit\"&gt;Mephit&lt;/a&gt; creatures.\nIt is considered an unenchanted item and deals 1d4 damage (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no animation assigned. The item has no other powers or abilities."}
{"id": "50422", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50422", "title": "B2-16.ITM", "text": "B2-16.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by various &lt;a href=\"Genie\"&gt;Genie&lt;/a&gt;'s, and the &lt;a href=\"Lesser%20Clay%20Golem\"&gt;Lesser Clay Golem&lt;/a&gt; and a few others. It is ostensibly a hammer, but it has no animation and doesn't respond to blunt weapon or hammer weapon proficiencies (if the equipping creature has those). It may be some kind of extrapolated fist bludgeoning attack.\nIt is considered a non-magical and unenchanted item and deals 2d8 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no animation assigned or other effects."}
{"id": "55778", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=55778", "title": "B2-24M3.ITM", "text": "B2-24M3.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by some creatures, such as the &lt;a href=\"Ice%20Golem\"&gt;Ice Golem&lt;/a&gt;. \nIt is considered an enchanted +3 item for purposes of what it can strike and inflicts 2d12 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; damage (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no specific animation assigned, or any other special abilities.\nMod content.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; mod boosts his weapon's range to 2 feet, which is what the mod calls a \"sensible' range for weaponry used by huge creatures like golems, who have a longer reach than a typical humanoid."}
{"id": "56165", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=56165", "title": "B3-12.ITM", "text": "The B3-12.ITM is an equipped item for various creatures as their melee attack weapon. It isn't droppable.\nEffects.\nThe non-magical and unenchanted weapon can inflict 3d4 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt;, and the user's &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; modifier can affect the damage.\nIt has no other abilities or special features."}
{"id": "51775", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51775", "title": "B3-18M3.ITM", "text": "B3-18M3.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by various &lt;a href=\"Genie\"&gt;Genie&lt;/a&gt;'s, and a few others. In fact, it's used by &lt;a href=\"Taquee\"&gt;Taquee&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Faafirah\"&gt;Faafirah&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt is ostensibly a scimitar, but it has no animation and doesn't respond to blunt weapon or weapon proficiencies (if the equipping creature has those). It may be some kind of extrapolated fist bludgeoning attack.\nIt is considered a magical and +3 enchanted item and deals 3d6 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no animation assigned or other effects."}
{"id": "50403", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50403", "title": "B3-24.ITM", "text": "B3-24.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by various creatures, including some &lt;a href=\"Genie\"&gt;Genie&lt;/a&gt;'s.\nIt is considered a non-magical and unenchanted item and applies 3d8 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; per hit, (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; bonus), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no animation assigned and other effects."}
{"id": "53086", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=53086", "title": "B4-32.ITM", "text": "B4-32.ITM is a weapon in \"\".\nEffects.\nThis item is given to creatures as a \"natural attack\", setting the amount of damage they do, in this case 4d8 crushing, which is also where it's name comes from Blunt4-32 damage."}
{"id": "56705", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=56705", "title": "B4-32M3.ITM", "text": "B4-32M3.ITM is a weapon in and .\nEffects.\nThis undroppable item is equipped by certain creatures as a \"natural attack\", perhaps a fist, used in melee attacks.\nThe weapon is a +3 &lt;a href=\"Enchanted%20item\"&gt;Enchanted item&lt;/a&gt;, with a melee attack range of 1, and a speed factor of 0.\nThe item inflicts 4d8 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; and can be modified by the user's &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; attribute.\nThe item has no other powers or abilities."}
{"id": "50043", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50043", "title": "B4-32M4.ITM", "text": "B4-32M4.ITM is an undroppable melee weapon used by various &lt;a href=\"Earth%20Elemental\"&gt;Earth Elemental&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Aerial%20servant%20%28creature%29\"&gt;Aerial servant (creature)&lt;/a&gt; beings.\nIt is considered a magical and +4 enchanted item and deals 4d8 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; modifier), with a range of one foot, and speed factor of 0.\nIt has no other effects."}
